nodes.text: Mo'rell was a male Tarasin, who lived on Cularin.

Mo'rell was a member of the Jaraana irstat and he lived with them in a village in the jungles of Cularin. By the time of the Clone Wars he was an elderly man. When the Dark Jedi Raik Muun set fire to the Jaraana irstat's village, Mo'rell was surrounded by burning rubble and the Heroes of Cularin attempted to rescue him.
